	<div style="text-align:right;">
		AGOSTINHO, Eduardo Luiz<sup>1</sup>; ALLEGRETTI, Ana Cristina Vidal<sup>2</sup>; MOYSES, Samuel Jorge<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
